</p>
<p>            
<strong>NON-DISCLOSURE OF INFORMATION.</strong> Sagicor does not share any nonpublic personal information with any nonaffiliated third parties, except in the following circumstances: As necessary to provide the service that the customer has requested or authorized, or to maintain, administer, and service the customer's account;
<ul>
