</p>
<p>Sagicor employees are prohibited, either during or after termination of their employment, from disclosing nonpublic personal information to any person or entity outside Sagicor, including family members, except under the circumstances described above. An employee is permitted to disclose nonpublic personal information only to such other employees who need to have access to such information to deliver our services to the customer.
</p>
<p>
